com.iopipe

Class IOpipeConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.iopipe.IOpipeConfiguration

  • public final class IOpipeConfiguration
extends Object
    This class contains the configuration for IOpipe and specifies the settings which are to be used when the server is contacted. This class is mutable.
    Since:
    2017/12/12
